# Cursor Rules for Funny Image Generator Project

## Package Manager
- Always use `pnpm` as the package manager for this project
- Use `pnpm install` instead of `npm install` or `yarn install`
- Use `pnpm add` instead of `npm install` or `yarn add`
- Use `pnpm dev` to start the development server

## Project Structure
- Keep source code organized in the `src/` directory
- Use TypeScript for all new files
- Follow Next.js 14+ conventions

## Code Style
- Use functional components with hooks
- Prefer arrow functions for components
- Use Tailwind CSS for styling
- Keep API routes in `src/pages/api/` or `src/app/api/`

## Environment Variables
- Store sensitive data in `.env.local`
- Never commit API keys to version control 